    "created_at": "2015-10-20T01:58:03Z",
    "updated_at": "2015-10-20T02:02:03Z",
    "body": "> If we are lucky we only need to change few lines to the original source code, and it will make future maintenance work easier.\n\nWe aren't lucky, I had to do a lot of changes to these files (https://github.com/atom/electron/compare/51ce39d...fb17ae ish, they expect a hardcoded \"Chrome.exe\" value, they do a bunch of things for Win8 Immersive Mode™, etc etc). It doesn't appear that they change too often though, and the interface to it is really simple, so worst comes to worst we can re-port it.\n"
  },
