    "updated_at": "2015-10-20T02:07:56Z",
    "body": "> We aren't lucky, I had to do a lot of changes to these files (they expect a hardcoded \"Chrome.exe\" value, they do a bunch of things for Win8 Immersive Mode™, etc etc). It doesn't appear that they change too often though, and the interface to it is really simple, so worst comes to worst we can re-port it.\n\nI still prefer to put the source code from chromium under `chromium_src` and keep their original names, so the changes to original files can be reduced to minimum, it really helped a lot in the past when doing upgrades to latest Chrome.\n"
