    "body": "@bpasero as I understand it, open-file is only invoked from the dock. This PR makes it so that there are now three ways to be signaled on OS X:\n1. `main.js` - your app started, it was the primary instance\n2. `open-file` / `open-url` - your app was run via Finder, it was a secondary instance. There was no command line arguments (because Finder)\n3. `makeSingleInstance` - your app was run via command-line, you get all the arguments and the working directory\n"
  },
